    <h1 class="header"> <span class="itemprop" itemprop="name">Philippe de Broca</span> 
        
        
        
            
            
                <span>(1933&ndash;2004)</span>
    </h1>
    
        <div class="infobar" id="name-job-categories">
            
            
<a href="#director"
onclick="nameJobCategoriesClickHandler(this)" > <span class="itemprop" itemprop="jobTitle">
Director</span></a>                 <span class="ghost">|</span> 
            
            
<a href="#writer"
onclick="nameJobCategoriesClickHandler(this)" > <span class="itemprop" itemprop="jobTitle">
Writer</span></a>                 <span class="ghost">|</span> 
            
            
<a href="#actor"
onclick="nameJobCategoriesClickHandler(this)" > <span class="itemprop" itemprop="jobTitle">
Actor</span></a>            
        </div>
    
        </div>
        </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Philippe de Broca was born on March 15, 1933 in Paris, France as Phillipe Claude Alex de Broca de Ferrussac. He was a director and writer, known for <a href="/title/tt0118756?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">Le bossu</a> (1997), <a href="/title/tt0058203?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">That Man from Rio</a> (1964) and <a href="/title/tt0070354?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">The Man from Acapulco</a> (1973). He was married to <a href="/name/nm0737733?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk4">Valérie Rojan</a> and <a href="/name/nm0452288?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk5">Margot Kidder</a>. He died on November 26, 2004 in Neuilly-sur-Seine, Hauts-de-Seine, France.            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0003606/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
    <div id="name-born-info" class="txt-block">
        <h4 class="inline">Born:</h4> 
<a href="/name/nm0003606/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bth_nm"
> Phillipe Claude Alex de Broca de Ferrussac
</a>            <br />
   
  <time datetime="1933-3-15" itemprop="birthDate">
<a href="/search/name?birth_monthday=3-15&refine=birth_monthday&ref_=nm_ov_bth_monthday"
>March 15</a>, 
     
<a href="/search/name?birth_year=1933&ref_=nm_ov_bth_year"
>1933</a>    
  </time>
            in
            <a href="/search/name?birth_place=Paris,+France&ref_=nm_ov_bth_place"
>Paris, France</a>
    </div>

<div id="name-death-info" class="txt-block">
    <h4 class="inline">Died:</h4> 
   
  <time datetime="2004-11-26" itemprop="deathDate">
<a href="/search/name?death_monthday=11-26&refine=death_monthday&ref_=nm_ov_dth_monthday"
>November 26</a>, 
     
<a href="/search/name?death_date=2004&ref_=nm_ov_dth_year"
>2004</a>    
  </time>
         (age 71) 
         in <a href="/search/name?death_place=Neuilly-sur-Seine,+Hauts-de-Seine,+France&ref_=nm_ov_dth_place"
