    <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
        <div id="dyk-trivia" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Trivia:</h4>
He directed 5 different actors in César-nominated performances: <a href="/name/nm0305368?ref_=nm_dyk_trv1">Nicole Garcia</a>, <a href="/name/nm0293889?ref_=nm_dyk_trv2">Stéphane Freiss</a>, <a href="/name/nm0000809?ref_=nm_dyk_trv3">Daniel Auteuil</a>, <a href="/name/nm0002100?ref_=nm_dyk_trv4">Marie Gillain</a> and <a href="/name/nm0001641?ref_=nm_dyk_trv5">Vincent Perez</a>. Garcia and Freiss won Césars for their performances in one of de Broca movies.                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0003606/bio?ref_=nm_dyk_trv_sm#trivia"
>See more</a>
                    </span>
                    &raquo;
        </div>
    
    
